CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1956, pg. 12 reads: "25th Anniversary - The Rev. and Mrs. Harold R. Tolliver, pastor of Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church, and his wife, admire the 25th anniversary cake, centerpiece of the June 17 celebration ,which honored them for a quarter century of service as pastor and "First Lady" of the church which was his first charge. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Men, women, and children, including Mrs. Harold R. Tolliver wearing polka dot dress,seated next to Rev. Harold R. Tolliver wearing striped necktie, and Rev. Leroy Patrick holding boy, gathered at banquet table in Grace Memorial Presbyterian Church for the Tolliver's 25th Anniversary
